parameters: Ah, what?! The treasure chest is empty!!!

They said there would be treasure in the dungeon-!! This is
a joke-!!
Let's go back to the village and consult with the guild.

For the return trip, let's use the wings of Utagae. We can
get back to the village in an instant♪
Let's go back to the village once and consult at the guild.

On our way back, let's use the wings of Utagae. We can
return to the village in an instant♪
By the way, why was there no treasure here in the end?
Why, I wonder. I have a strange feeling in my chest...!!
